Class Summary 
Class Description
HikingHistoryEntry
This class represents a hike that a user has completed.
HikingHistoryStorageContainer
This class provides storage and organizational functionality for HikingHistoryEntry objects.
LinkedListUserStorageContainer Deprecated.
This class is superceded by the TreeMapUserStorageContainer, which has already been proven to be more efficient.
PointOfInterest
This class represents any waypoints (points of interest) that can be found on a particular trail.
PointOfInterestStorageContainer
This class provides storage and organizational functionality for PointOfInterest objects.
Trail
This class represents a trail.
TrailStorageContainer
This class provides storage and organizational functionality for Trail objects.
TreeMapUserStorageContainer
This class provides storage and authentication capabilities for User objects.
User
This class represents a user's account.
